<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Thank You</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            color: #333;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #fff;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            border-radius: 8px;
        }

        h2 {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #007bff;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
        }

        .card-image {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

            .card-image img {
                max-width: 100px;
                height: auto;
            }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h2>Thank You!</h2>
        <p>Thank you for your purchase! You have successfully completed your transaction.</p>
        <div class="card-image">
            <img src="credit-card-placeholder.png" alt="Credit Card Image" />
        </div>
        <p>We appreciate your business and hope to serve you again soon.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
